<T>__{camera moves out the window and up to:}
<A>__{watters in the hotel window across the way, sniper rifle snug to her shoulder, eye on the scope, waiting for the word.}
<B>__{camera moves through rifle scope up to and inside earpiece}
<A>__{inside the earpiece at 10000x normal magnification; micro sound condensers and circuits the size of skyscrapers. then, a voice makes the landscape tremble, like the trump of god:}
<C>__{sykes}
<D>__{bring it.}
<B>__{the camera suddenly reverses path}
<A>__{back out of the earpiece, down through the scope, over the barrel of the rifle...boom...a .50 caliber bullet is birthed.}
